data.Summary:
As a sales leader, I have shown a commitment to spearheading initiatives that significantly enhance productivity and team performance. Through team collaboration I have driven notable revenue growth and customer retention across Southern California, managing a substantial revenue portfolio to secure positive financial outcomes.

With expertise in operations management and data analysis, I've crafted innovative strategies that propelled corporate expansion and facilitated a culture of high performance. My dedication to personalized coaching has empowered leaders, cultivating team cohesion and maximizing overall performance.

positions.Title: District Manager
positions.Description:
Spearheaded initiatives to build high-performing sales teams and drive productivity. Proficient in analyzing sales and operational data to develop innovative strategies that accelerate revenue growth. Committed to fostering a culture of collaboration and accountability, while delivering tailored coaching to maximize individual and team performance.

Notable Achievements:

•  Streamlined operations across 22 locations, growing revenue and improving retention.
•  Managed a $110M revenue portfolio P&L, driving positive financial outcomes.
•  Achieved impressive growth: 193% in EBITDA, 215% in operating profit, and up to 12.4% in revenue.

positions.Title: Operations Manager
positions.Description:
Lead all operations, driving operational efficiency. Responsible for leading, developing, and engaging a team of exceptional talent, enabling innovation; Focused on motivating, mentoring, and coaching the team to become effective leaders. Leveraged creative problem solving, interpreting big data, and delivered meaningful results that drive productivity and efficiency.

Notable Achievements:

•  Maintained a 20% performance improvement rate in associates through coaching, mentoring, and 
     corrective actions.
•  Leveraged effective productivity planning, forecasting, and labor allocation to optimize performance. 
•  Led a team of 7 Area Managers and 300 hourly associates, achieving 15% productivity growth through strong leadership, development, and engagement strategies, enhancing operational efficiency.
•  Reduced safety incident rate by 15% by implementing and maintaining robust safety programs, ensuring OSHA compliance and a safe workplace for all staff.

positions.Title: District Manager
positions.Description:
Led talent recognition initiatives and delivered tailored developmental pathways to nurture top performers within the management framework. Pioneered forward-thinking sales tactics and customer relationship management methodologies to enhance client acquisition endeavors.

Notable Achievements:

•  Enhanced sales growth through monthly business reviews, KPI evaluation, and implementation.
•  Reduced member attrition by 1% with tailored retention strategies and personalized engagement.
•  Launched new studios, raising sales targets by 50% through innovative approaches.
•  Boosted studio revenue by optimizing business tactics, workflows, and resource allocation.

positions.Title: General Manager
positions.Description:
Focused on talent development, nurturing internal candidates for advancement while ensuring prompt resolution of customer inquiries. Managed inventory, equipment, and facility upgrades to maintain cleanliness, safety, and member satisfaction. Lead community engagement initiatives and partnerships to enhance brand visibility and customer relationships. 

Notable Achievements:

• Drove $8M sales growth leading a team of 5 managers and 60+ associates across three departments.
• Ranked top 10 in Gallup Q12 Employee Engagement, showcasing leadership in enhancing productivity.
• Boosted profits by 5% and ranked top 3 regionally for profitability through operational efficiency.

positions.Title: Sales Manager
positions.Description:
Successfully lead team to surpass revenue goals through strategy development, team motivation, and client relationship management. Drive sales growth and optimize processes. Deliver an outstanding customer experience achieving organizational objectives. 

Notable Achievements:

•  Achieved $1 million in personal sales revenue.
•  Grew revenue by 34%. Met profitability & sales metrics.
•  Exceeded key metrics for 14 consecutive months (2010-2011).

positions.Title: Fitness Manager
positions.Description:
Deliver results by leading a high performing team of Personal Trainers to drive revenue and profitability. Demonstrate passion about fitness and dedication to helping clients achieve goals through effective coaching and education. Leverage strong leadership, communication, and sales skills.

Notable Achievements:

•  Increased revenue by 20% within the first year through sales management and client retention efforts. 
•  Developed a team of 20 Coaches, of which, three were promoted to leadership positions.
•  Exceeded revenue targets, achieving an average monthly increase of 25% over a two-year period.

positions.Title: United States Marine
positions.Description:
The United States Marine Corps (USMC) is a branch of the United States Armed Forces responsible for providing power projection, using the mobility of the United States Navy, by Congressional mandate, to deliver rapidly, combined-arms task forces on land, at sea, and in the air.

Notable Achievements:

•  Awarded the Combat Action Ribbon for actively participating in ground combat.
•  Earned the Marine Corps Good Conduct Medal for exemplary conduct.
•  Participated in Operations Iraqi and Enduring Freedom, showcasing bravery and dedication.
